      <title>中国不降息是为了应对未来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/china-keeps-key-rate-steady-with-traders-expecting-cuts-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国没有降息，而是利用一年期政策工具释放了2014年以来最多的资金，为明年中美贸易紧张局势可能升级做好准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-25/china-keeps-key-rate-steady-with-traders-expecting-cuts-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 01:48:15 GMT</pubDate>
